room_title: Escape room "Miner Problems" by GTFO Escape Room in South Portland
review: I've been to GTFO a few different times and trapped in a horror movie and the Magician's room were fun, but the Miners room was truly EPIC! Kept my group on their toes the entire time and with 8 of us, it was rare that anyone was not doing something. Highly recommended to anyone who likes a good escape room!

room_title: Escape room "Miner Problems" by GTFO Escape Room in South Portland
review: Great time! We did 'Miner Problems' and it was challenging and fun! Would go back again!
